Premium quality Traminer (croatian:Traminac) has pronounced variety specific characteristics, as well as fresh and original features. Thanks to the extremely suitable microclimate, the Kutjevo Traminac has a soft secondary bouquet of pronounced flowery and fruity notes. Traminac is an excellent aperitif wine, and its advantages become fully expressed when served with sweet desserts. It is served cooled at 10-12 °C.

Currently, we ship to addresses in member states of the EU except Finland and Sweden . We offer free shipping from an amount of 150€ per shipping in Austria (250€ in Germany).

Free home delivery within Vienna is possible with an invoiced value of goods of 75 euros and more.
